name: 原神散兵的LORA （LORA form Wanderer of Genshin Impac）
description:
我训练的散兵的LORA，经测试，真人和二次模型效果都还不错，但某C开头的网红真人模型生成不出少年脸.....正常使用并不需要降低权重。但如果需要一些“奇怪”的姿式，请降低权重。

请自行娱乐，不要用于谋利。

The LORA model I trained for scattered soldiers has been tested and has produced good results for both real people and second models. However, the real-person model beginning with a "C" cannot generate a young face... Normal use does not require weight reduction. However, if you need some "strange" poses, please lower the weight.

Please enjoy for personal use only and do not use for commercial purposes.

Because my English is very poor, the above translation comes from ChatGPT, and accuracy cannot be guaranteed
